{
  "stem": "20616.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was the time of the Depression here in the United States and he would have to get a-- a guarantee from someone that we would not become public burdens.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, it was very difficult during the Depression to find someone who would give you a guarantee because here comes somebody who is not trained except as a lawyer, has no other possible means of making a living, no prospects, whose wife has never worked before, he's got a child in school.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's very risky for someone to give.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father was unable to find anyone to give him an affidavit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had some names and some people to visit, regards to give, and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a day or two before he was to come back, unsuccessfully, he visited some-- someone who has a realty business and wanted to give him regards from a friend or far-fetched relative.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they had a talk and my father said, you know, I'm trying very hard to come to the United States and I was trying to get that affidavit and nobody would give it to me.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, what, nobody would give you the affidavit?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Said, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I've exhausted all my possibilities, I have no one else to ask.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Said, well, ?] you didn't ask me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Said, well, I don't know you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm just here to give you some-- I wouldn't dare to-- to impose upon you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, if you need an affidavit, I'll be happy to give it to you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he gave him the affidavit and when he came back, we made plans to emigrate to the United States.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, there was a waiting time, there was a quota.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
